&gt; or<br>&gt; mpirun -np 4 -machinefile machines.list mpi_executable<br>&gt;<br>&gt; where machines.list contains a list of your computers identified by their<br>&gt; host names.<br>&gt; The former command should run the program locally on 2 processors/cores, the<br>
